Usage:
Use API Gateway (AWS API Gateway, Kong, Apigee).

How it works:
Mobile App â†’ API Gateway â†’ Microservices

Example:

GET /user/profile â†’ routes to user-service
POST /order â†’ routes to order-service
API Gateway can:

Validate JWT token

Block too many requests

Add headers

Convert output

Log analytics

